Subject: wifi: ath11k: support IPQ9574

The IPQ9574 can expose its integrated Wi-Fi device over AHB. Add the
hardware description needed by ath11k and match the IPQ9574 DT compatible.

Reuse the IPQ8074 CE configuration and IPQ6018 service mapping as described
by the upstream IPQ9574 ath11k series and the downstream cnss2/qca-wifi-host-cmn
mapping.

Adapt the change to the OpenWrt backports-6.18 ath11k hardware parameter
layout.

Signed-off-by: Alexandru Gagniuc <mr.nuke.me@gmail.com>
Signed-off-by: Igor Kravchenko <igor.kravchenko05@gmail.com>
---
--- a/drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath11k/ahb.c
+++ b/drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath11k/ahb.c
@@ -25,6 +25,9 @@ static const struct of_device_id ath11k_
 	/* TODO: Should we change the compatible string to something similar
 	 * to one that ath10k uses?
 	 */
+	{ .compatible = "qcom,ipq9574-wifi",
+	  .data = (void *)ATH11K_HW_IPQ9574,
+	},
 	{ .compatible = "qcom,ipq8074-wifi",
 	  .data = (void *)ATH11K_HW_IPQ8074,
